<actions>
  <update-node tree="member_expression: votePrice != data.currentMode &&             data.voteFrequency[votePrice].isGreaterThan [1613,1701]" label="votePrice >  data.currentMode ||             data.voteFrequency[votePrice].isGreaterThan" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: data.totalVotes.isGreaterThan(minVoteThreshold) &&             data.voteFrequency[data.currentMode].div(data.totalVotes).isGreaterThan [2869,3003]" label="data.totalVotes.isGreaterThan(minVoteThreshold) ||             data.voteFrequency[data.currentMode].div(data.totalVotes).isGreaterThan" />
  <update-node tree="comparison_operator: == [3762,3764]" label="<=" />
</actions>
